# D{{N}} — Strategic Classification Heatmap

**Audience:** Stakeholder + Architect (positioning conversations).
**When to look at this:** When deciding where to invest, what to outsource, what to build off-the-shelf. Quarterly portfolio reviews.
**Prose gap closed:** `5-bc-candidates.md` lists the Core/Supporting/Generic hint per BC; this diagram shows the **distribution** in one frame so trade-offs are visible at a glance.

