## Legend

| Quadrant | Strategic class | Investment posture |
|----------|-----------------|--------------------|
| Q1 (top-right) | Core | Build in-house; senior engineers; protect the model |
| Q2 (top-left) | Strategic Supporting | Build to standard; outsource if cheaper |
| Q3 (bottom-left) | Generic | Buy / rent; do not staff senior |
| Q4 (bottom-right) | Differentiator at risk | Re-classify or de-fund — mismatch between team belief and business reality |

